snippet.title: Germany vs. Belgium Highlights | FOX Soccer
snippet.description:
Germany and Belgium faced off in a 2023 international friendly held in Germany. Belgium took close control from the jump and was able to get on the board in the sixth minute after Yannick Carrasco struck the high center of the goal. Three minutes later, Belgium‚Äôs Romelu Lukaku put up goal number two after another strike to the center of the goal. Just before halftime, Germany found their first after Niclas F√ºllkrug converted the penalty. In the 78th minute, Kevin De Bruyne fired in Belgium‚Äôs third and final goal. Germany was able to secure their second in the 87th after a wonderful finish by Serge Gnabry, however Belgium would remain victorious for a 3-2 finish.

snippet.title: NEW Lamborghini Revuelto: 1,000bhp V12 Hybrid Aventador Successor | Top Gear
snippet.description:
Here it is, the long awaited Aventador replacement. It is, inevitably, a plug-in hybrid, but it‚Äôs one that takes the possibilities of the format and does wild and wonderful things with it. 

We‚Äôre talking a naturally aspirated 6.5-litre V12, aided by three electric motors, two of which are mounted on the front axle, the third integrated into the new eight-speed dual-clutch transmission. 

All of that means the Revuelto is good for a total power output of 1,001bhp, a top speed of 217mph and 0-62mph in just 2.5 seconds. Yes, the line between Hypercar and Supercar is well and truly blurred.

Top Gear Magazine‚Äôs Editor, Jack Rix, gives us the full tour.

snippet.title: Elemental | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This Summer, meet the residents of Element City

Watch the new trailer for Disney and Pixar‚Äôs #Elemental and see the movie in 3D, only in theaters June 16!

Check out a brand-new trailer for Disney and Pixar‚Äôs ‚ÄúElemental,‚Äù an all-new original feature film that transports moviegoers to an extraordinary place called Element City, where a host of elements live and work. The trailer showcases each element‚Äîair, earth, water and fire‚Äîand what sets them apart according to Ember, a quick-witted and fiery woman who‚Äôs always stayed close to home in Firetown. In ‚ÄúElemental,‚Äù which opens in theaters on June 16, she finally ventures out of her comfort zone to explore this spectacular world born from the imaginations of Pixar‚Äôs filmmakers and specifically crafted for the big-screen experience.
